OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy, with this thickening overnight
OL,7,Fto produce hill fog by the early hours
OL,8,Fof Tuesday. Outbreaks of rain at
OL,9,Ftimes, particularly over hills.
OL,10,FStaying mild under the blanket of
OL,11,Fcloud with light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FMurky to start on Tuesday
OL,14,Fwith some light showers. A few
OL,15,Fbrighter spells possible for a time,
OL,16,Fbefore a spell of rain arrives to end
OL,17,Fthe day. Warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
